==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fub
<hw>Fub</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[The same word as <ets>fob</ets> to
cheat.]</ety> <def>To put off by trickery; to cheat.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I have been <qex>fubbed</qex> off, and <qex>fubbed</qex> off, and
fabbed off, from this day to that day.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

